<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6 step">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2">
        <div class="step-no">
          <strong>1</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 step-content">
        <h3>控制面板</h3>
        <p>点击电脑屏幕左下角的“开始”，再点击“控制面板”，进入控制面板的设置</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img alt="点击电脑屏幕左下角的“开始”，再点击“控制面板”，进入控制面板的设置" class="img-border loader" src="/assets/steps/windows_xp/l2tp/step1-5abe78b4768d423bee189a5b4c6a2996.jpg" title="控制面板" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6 step">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2">
        <div class="step-no">
          <strong>2</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 step-content">
        <h3>网络和 Internet 连接</h3>
        <p>点击“网络和 Internet 连接”文字，进入网络和 Internet 连接的设置</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img alt="点击“网络和 Internet 连接”文字，进入网络和 Internet 连接的设置" class="img-border loader" src="/assets/steps/windows_xp/l2tp/step2-cff2ddbd6b193f1ff86bc1580692e858.jpg" title="网络和 Internet 连接" />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6 step">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2">
        <div class="step-no">
          <strong>3</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 step-content">
        <h3>创建到您的工作位置的网络连接</h3>
        <p>点击“创建⼀个到您的工作位置的网络连接”文字</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img alt="点击“创建⼀个到您的工作位置的网络连接”文字" class="img-border loader" src="/assets/steps/windows_xp/l2tp/step3-2740352c50ac21b2c0d7afa4925422a1.jpg" title="创建⼀个到您的工作位置的网络连接" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6 step">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2">
        <div class="step-no">
          <strong>4</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 step-content">
        <h3>虚拟专用网络连接</h3>
        <p>选择“虚拟专用网络连接”，点击“下一步”按钮</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img alt="选择“虚拟专用网络连接”，点击“下一步”按钮" class="img-border loader" src="/assets/steps/windows_xp/l2tp/step4-a1041520dec66b29dba1b63e887ac690.jpg" title="虚拟专用网络连接" />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6 step">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2">
        <div class="step-no">
          <strong>5</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 step-content">
        <h3>公司名</h3>
        <p>“公司名”中填入“云梯 VPN (L2TP)”；然后点击“下一步”按钮</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img alt="公司名中填入云梯 VPN (L2TP)；然后点击下一步按钮" class="img-border loader" src="/assets/steps/windows_xp/l2tp/step5-e429b297879d5a1e711e671f38a4e8f1.jpg" title="公司名" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6 step">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2">
        <div class="step-no">
          <strong>6</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 step-content">
        <h3>主机名或 IP 地址</h3>
        <p>“主机名或 IP 地址”中填入服务器域名（<a href="/admin/servers" target="_blank">前往服务器列表页面查看</a>）；然后点击“下一步”按钮</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img alt="“主机名或 IP 地址”中填入服务器域名（前往服务器列表页面查看）；然后点击“下一步”按钮" class="img-border loader" src="/assets/steps/windows_xp/l2tp/step6-6e4ae7e8054f06d6be4e8ef12b7ca9e4.jpg" title="主机名或 IP 地址" />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6 step">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2">
        <div class="step-no">
          <strong>7</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 step-content">
        <h3>添加快捷方式，完成</h3>
        <p>勾选“在我的桌面上添加一个到此连接的快捷方式”，然后点击“完成”按钮</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img alt="勾选“在我的桌面上添加一个到此连接的快捷方式”，然后点击“完成”按钮" class="img-border loader" src="/assets/steps/windows_xp/l2tp/step7-0b0bc2eac1aca0385545621a8d067376.jpg" title="添加快捷方式，完成" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6 step">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2">
        <div class="step-no">
          <strong>8</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 step-content">
        <h3>网络连接</h3>
        <p>回到“网络和 Internet 连接”，点击“网络连接”文字</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img alt="回到“网络和 Internet 连接”，点击“网络连接”文字" class="img-border loader" src="/assets/steps/windows_xp/l2tp/step8-8220fab1638f37d661cfab030d66011b.jpg" title="网络连接" />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6 step">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2">
        <div class="step-no">
          <strong>9</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 step-content">
        <h3>双击连接</h3>
        <p>在“虚拟专用网络”里看到之前新建的“云梯 VPN (L2TP)”，双击图标，打开连接窗口</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img alt="在虚拟专用网络里看到之前新建的云梯 VPN (L2TP)，双击图标，打开连接窗口" class="img-border loader" src="/assets/steps/windows_xp/l2tp/step9-2cd90eb50e85707a659a9d5ec690cec1.jpg" title="双击连接" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6 step">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2">
        <div class="step-no">
          <strong>10</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 step-content">
        <h3>属性</h3>
        <p>点击“属性”按钮</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img alt="点击“属性”按钮" class="img-border loader" src="/assets/steps/windows_xp/l2tp/step10-cc13b33108669d279f1d4b2f8ffcdef9.jpg" title="属性" />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6 step">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2">
        <div class="step-no">
          <strong>11</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 step-content">
        <h3>VPN 类型</h3>
        <p>点击上方“网络”标签，“VPN 类型”栏中选择“L2TP IPSec VPN”</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img alt="点击上方“网络”标签，“VPN 类型”栏中选择“L2TP IPSec VPN”" class="img-border loader" src="/assets/steps/windows_xp/l2tp/step11-00344acd0104e653f2b25a1ba13ed460.jpg" title="VPN 类型" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6 step">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2">
        <div class="step-no">
          <strong>12</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 step-content">
        <h3>IPSec 设置</h3>
        <p>点击上方“安全”标签，点击“IPSec 设置”按钮</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img alt="点击上方“安全”标签，点击“IPSec 设置”按钮" class="img-border loader" src="/assets/steps/windows_xp/l2tp/step12-fc70431d2275b18746437419abe63f22.jpg" title="IPSec 设置" />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6 step">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2">
        <div class="step-no">
          <strong>13</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 step-content">
        <h3>密钥</h3>
        <p>“密钥”中填入具体密钥（<a href="/admin" target="_blank">前往我的云梯首页查看共享密钥</a>）；然后点击”确定“按钮</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img alt="“密钥”中填入具体密钥（前往我的云梯首页查看共享密钥）；然后点击”确定“按钮" class="img-border loader" src="/assets/steps/windows_xp/l2tp/step13-3d7fc22f1996e38eda30927e83b49882.jpg" title="密钥" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6 step">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2">
        <div class="step-no">
          <strong>14</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 step-content">
        <h3>用户名和密码</h3>
        <p>“用户名”中填入你的VPN帐号用户名；“密码”中填入你的VPN帐号密码；然后点击”连接“按钮</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img alt="“用户名”中填入你的VPN帐号用户名；“密码”中填入你的VPN帐号密码；然后点击”连接“按钮" class="img-border loader" src="/assets/steps/windows_xp/l2tp/step14-f09fabe6a6ee615111a449795e56361b.jpg" title="用户名和密码" />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6 step">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2">
        <div class="step-no">
          <strong>15</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 step-content">
        <h3>连接中</h3>
        <p class="height3">连接中</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img alt="连接中" class="img-border loader" src="/assets/steps/windows_xp/l2tp/step15-c2553c57e59804c921b65bc6c58bd366.jpg" title="连接中" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6 step">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2">
        <div class="step-no">
          <strong>16</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 step-content">
        <h3>快速连接，断开</h3>
        <p class="height3">右键点击 VPN 桌面快捷方式，看到“云梯 VPN (L2TP)”的连接状态，通过“断开”或“连接”按钮，方便快速断开或连接 VPN</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img alt="右键点击 VPN 桌面快捷方式，看到云梯 VPN (L2TP)的连接状态，通过断开或连接按钮，方便快速断开或连接 VPN" class="img-border loader" src="/assets/steps/windows_xp/l2tp/step16-7d29b539fd869701ecd77efd6e082ee3.jpg" title="快速连接，断开" />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6 step">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2">
        <div class="step-no">
          <strong>17</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 step-content">
        <h3>打开本地连接属性</h3>
        <p class="height3">在“控制面板 -> 网络和 Internet 连接 -> 网络连接”中找到“本地连接”，右键点击，然后点击“属性”；点击"Internet 协议（TCP/IP）"，点击“属性”按钮</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img alt="在“控制面板 -&gt; 网络和 Internet 连接 -&gt; 网络连接”中找到“本地连接”，右键点击，然后点击“属性”；点击&quot;Internet 协议（TCP/IP）&quot;，点击“属性”按钮" class="img-border loader" src="/assets/steps/windows_xp/l2tp/step17-445905cc635d7faedf4c642ac128ef44.jpg" title="打开本地连接属性" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6 step">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2">
        <div class="step-no">
          <strong>18</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 step-content">
        <h3>设置 DNS，防止 DNS 污染</h3>
        <p class="height3">选中“使用下面的 DNS 服务器地址”，“首选 DNS 服务器”中填写 8.8.8.8，“备用 DNS 服务器”中填写 8.8.4.4，然后点击“确定”按钮</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img alt="选中“使用下面的 DNS 服务器地址”，“首选 DNS 服务器”中填写 8.8.8.8，“备用 DNS 服务器”中填写 8.8.4.4，然后点击“确定”按钮" class="img-border loader" src="/assets/steps/windows_xp/l2tp/step18-8725f7dc81e0f44db9dbf48aeb2c5726.jpg" title="设置 DNS，防止 DNS 污染" />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6 step">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2">
        <div class="step-no">
          <strong>19</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 step-content">
        <h3>清除 DNS 缓存</h3>
        <p>在“开始 -> 所有程序 -> 附件”中找到并打开“命令提示符”，输入以下命令并回车：ipconfig /flushdns</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img alt="在“开始 -&gt; 所有程序 -&gt; 附件”中找到并打开“命令提示符”，输入以下命令并回车：ipconfig /flushdns" class="img-border loader" src="/assets/steps/windows_xp/l2tp/step19-858c2d8ca7523d68724c316332383be2.jpg" title="清除 DNS 缓存" />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
  
